<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.10.10">
<l>naṟaicey poḻilmaḻaita vaḻumnanti puravaṇṇa karamnaṇṇi yuṟaiyum</l>
<l>uṟaikoḷ pukarāḻi curicaṅka mavaiyaṅkai yuṭaiyāṉai yoḷicēr</l>
<l>kaṟaiva ḷarumvēlval lakaliya ṉolimālai yivaiyaintu maintum</l>
<l>muṟaiyi lavaipayila valavaṭiya varkaḷkoṭuvi ṉaikaḷmuḻuta kalumē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Devotees who are able to recite these five-and-five [verses] in order,</l>
<l>This garland of words of Kaliyaṉ, skilled with the bright spear</l>
<l rend="indent">where [blood]stains linger,</l>
<l>About the one who has fine hands with a spiraled conch</l>
<l rend="indent">and an excellent, bright discus,</l>
<l>Who went and dwelled in Nantipura Viṇṇakaram where mist creeps</l>
<l rend="indent">through nectar-filled groves, all of [their] harsh fate will vanish.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
